column2: SELECT TOP # p.obj,  str(p.ra,#,#) as ra,  str(p.[dec],#,#) as dec,  p.dered_g as g,  p.dered_r as r,  p.dered_i as i,  p.dered_z as z,  str(g-r, #,#), str(g-i, #,#), str(r-i, #,#),  p.petroR5#_g,p.petroR5#_r,p.petroR5#_i,  p.petroR9#_g,p.petroR9#_r,p.petroR9#_i,  ISNULL(s.z,#) as z,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as zErr,  ISNULL(s.zWarning,#) as zWarning,ISNULL(s.class,#) as class,   p.score as score,  c.z,c.zErr FROM BESTDR1#..Galaxy AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN BESTDR1#..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) AS b ON b.objID = P.objID  JOIN Photoz AS c ON c.objID = P.objID  WHERE g < # AND r < # AND i < # AND z < #
